snippet.title: Snipperclips Plus: Cut It Out Together! - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Paper pals Snip and Clip must cut each other into the right shapes to overcome tricky obstacles in this updated version of the game. Partner up with friends and family to solve puzzles, including new comic book and toy box worlds, 3 new Blitz Mode multiplayer activities, and a Stamp mode for creating art. Plus, play the original levels in new shapes!

Snipperclips Plus DLC is Available 11/10! : https://goo.gl/7FAsdU
